channel.title: I need ₤200 In the next 3 months, any idears?
channel.description:
It´s not really a question, it´s more like i need suggestions, thats why i didn´t put this in the question section, please read through it FULLY before posting a reply.
Here is my problem:
I am 12 years old and need a job, or something that can make 200 pounds in 3 months so i can afford my new computer. I already have 100 pounds saved, but need 200, and my b´d money so i can get a pretty good computer for 500-550pounds. I know how would just say "get a job" but i need you to explain into that, i´m 12 years old so i can´t get a job from anywhere, I was thinking of doing the paperround but some other guy has been doing that for 9 years and won´t hand to job over to me, No silly comments please, be aware i have school days, are 12 years old and can´t do the paper round.
Any suggestions?
Thanks in advance,
